Global Generic Injection Market Insights
Generic Injection Market size was valued at USD 42.50 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 75.00 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Generic Injection Market Overview
The global generic injection market has shown significant growth, reaching a market value of USD 44.67 billion in 2024 and is expected to continue growing at a healthy CAGR through the forecast period. The rising prevalence of chronic diseases, such as cancer and diabetes, along with increasing patient demand for affordable healthcare, have been key factors driving market growth. The market is driven by the growing preference for biologic drug substitutes and generic drugs due to their cost-effectiveness. Furthermore, favorable government policies and initiatives aimed at reducing healthcare costs are expected to foster market expansion. By 2030, the market size is anticipated to surpass USD 85 billion.

